title: Francesco Mussin
text:
Welcome to my personal site. I put a number of things in here, including my projects, my personal notes on various topics, and more(?)


I’m a mathematics students in the Master’s degree program at ETH Zurich.




I’m currently studying at ETH Zurich
I’ve graduated in Mathematics at Università degli Studi di Milano-Bicocca
I’ve received my high school diploma in Milan at Liceo Scientifico Piero Bottoni

title: Personal Notes
text: Throughout my academic carreer I have been making LaTeX notes on essentially every course I took. This was a way to store everything I needed to know digitally. Too much later I realized that the best way to do that was with a site, so here we are: no more phisical notebooks or tex files that aren’t stored on all my devices, here I can access everything I want.
